The durable rubber handle offers a comfortable grip and is built to withstand long term repeated use. It comes with a black nylon sheath to cover the blade when not in use. MTech USA offers a diversified lineup of tactical folding knives, fixed blade knives, archery products, and security items -- all at competitive prices.
